{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/header_steam1_wishlist.png?t=1732757980\" /></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/header_steam1_main.png?t=1732757980\" /></p>Become the ultimate manager of tomorrow's superstars with &quot;K-Pop!&quot;, an addictive clicker game created by stans for stans! Gather billions of fans, unlock idols at every milestone, compare your score with your friends and become the ultimate k-pop manager. <br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/header_steam1_idols.png?t=1732757980\" /></p>Trade idol cards with your friends and with the community on the marketplace, display your collection on your Steam profile! Show us your rarest bias! <br><br><strong>Play 3 hours to collect idols across six levels of rarity:</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Common</li><li>Uncommon</li><li>Rare</li><li>Epic</li><li>Legendary</li><li>Genuine</li></ul><br><strong>At every milestone, a new random idol joins your group!</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>100 fans</li><li>1000 fans</li><li>10.000 fans</li><li>100.000 fans</li><li>1.000.000 fans</li><li>10.000.000 fans</li><li>100.000.000 fans</li><li>1.000.000.000 fans</li><li>10.000.000.000 fans</li><li>100.000.000.000 fans</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/header_steam1_updates.png?t=1732757980\" /></p>Play during regular updates and special events that introduce new idols and cards based on real-life events, such as album releases, concerts, anniversaries, and fan meetings. Stay tuned for exclusive content when your favorite groups release new music or celebrate milestones!